<h1 class="font-size:40px font-weight:800 line-height:1">
  Rule 5: Pseudo class
</h1>
<p class="md-info">Your can use all Pseudo class:</p>
<p class="md-code">
  hover:background:hsl(200,50%,45%)
</p>
<p class="md-code">
  before:content:'Hello'
</p>
<p class="md-info">Your can use CSS selector + Pseudo class:</p>
<p class="md-code">
  div>ul:hover:background:#00f
</p>
<p class="md-info">Pseudo-classes with parameters are not supported:</p>
<p class="md-code">
  not(.dog):background:#00f  //error
</p>
